title: Complimentary package receiving, Walk-in closets, Dog park
posting_body: ['This re-invented collection of spacious one, two and three bedroom apartment homes in Las Vegas were thoughtfully crafted with every possible lifestyle in mind.', 'You’ll appreciate the designer kitchen fixtures & counter tops, upgraded cabinets and the latest and greatest in stainless steel appliances.', 'Stroll along the rich wood plank flooring and explore your spacious walk-in closets and ultra-modern bathrooms.', 'Exhale as you step out onto your 12-foot balcony and take in the view of the buzzing Las Vegas Strip and watch the sun setting behind the mountains.', 'Schedule a tour today.', '-Personal laundry center on every floor', '-Resort-style 9 foot deep pool and recreation deck', '-Designer selected lighting fixtures', '-Dog park', '-Expansive fitness center with free weights, cardio equipment, exercise balls and yoga mats', '-Durable granite counter tops', '-Complimentary package receiving', '-Move-in Deposit Free with Jetty', '-Panoramic Las Vegas Strip Views', '-12-foot balconies offering Las Vegas Strip views and Mountain views', '-Stainless Steel appliances', '-Short Term Lease', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Equal housing opportunity*']
